        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-10039 mb-requirement-id-10055">
        <strong>Option 6: Baseball Throw</strong><br /><i>Resource:</i>
        <a
          href="https://youtu.be/UHRU973uu2c?si=eu9KwMfgqkKxrSCK"
          target="_blank"
          >How to Throw a Baseball (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-10055 mb-requirement-id-10056">
        (a) Baseball throw for accuracy, 10 throws at a target (distance to be
        determined by age): ages 11 to 12, 20 feet; ages 13 to 15, 30 feet; ages
        16 to 17, 40 feet
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-10055 mb-requirement-id-10057">
        (b) Baseball throw for distance, five throws (total distance)
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-10039 mb-requirement-id-10058">
        <strong>Option 7: Basketball Shooting</strong><br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a
          href="https://youtu.be/iW2VFzBiaQo?si=OcW1PTb8DR3ZtR6y"
          target="_blank"
          >How to Shoot a Free Throw (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a
          href="https://youtu.be/q4IqeXob_qg?si=or8nQWc5bXpIOEQe"
          target="_blank"
          >How to Shoot a Layup (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a
          href="https://youtu.be/UcnB9e5O5NY?si=dlC30TAj-AyuKca9"
