        <a
          href="https://youtu.be/vJ3BHM9U-S0?si=xCzYWo3YkxdOXkfu"
          target="_blank"
          >Kick a Football Field Goal (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-10039 mb-requirement-id-10064">
        <strong>Option 9: Weight Training</strong>
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-10064 mb-requirement-id-10065">
        (a) Chest/bench press, two sets of 15 repetitions each <br /><i
          >Resource:</i
        >
        <a
          href="https://youtu.be/bt-yRU4HEZ4?si=Jw0QKVOvUsgcIKGa"
